berries and whipped cream (optional)."}],"hintsAndTricks":["If you’re watching calories, you’re best to choose (freshly) whipped cream over double cream. It has almost one-third of the calories and one-third of the fat of the same volume of double cream.","If you prefer, you can use extra virgin olive oil instead of the coconut oil. Add it to the mixing bowl at the same time as the maple syrup."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","40m","6 portions"]}